title: The Super Prospect & the Punch
description:
The guys give you all the NFL previews you can handle, get into Thursday Night's horrific football game, and much, much more -- but that's now why you're here. You want to hear about Draymond Green punching Jordan Poole. Jalen takes us behind the curtain, talks about the difference between a fight, a teammate fight, and a suckerpunch, and lets you know what this means for both players, and the franchise going forward. And! We got a second nationally televised taste of Victor Wembanyama, and it was sweeter than the first! Is this the greatest prospect in the history of the game???
